Just touchdown in #congo it feels so special to be back @malaikadrc after 7years when I visited in 2016 the school had 230 students and built 5 wells. Fast forward to now, over 430 students receive free education, plus Malaika has built and refurbished 30 wells  to support the wider community! It’s mind blowing to witness the incredible progress made! #MalaikaDRC #Malakiaclassof23
Me and the #classof2023 🩷

#photodump of my trip to #congo and @malaikadrc #graduation with my #sister @noellacoursaris 🩷❤️ Not only do they provide free education to the girls but @ the community Center, there are classes in electronics, mechanics and plumbing to help people in the wider community gain skills to get jobs 🙌🏾
